Two people were injured after a drunk driver crashed into an electricity post at Ol Kalou town on Tuesday evening.Nderitu Njagi was driving from Mugumo, Githunguri sub-location. His vehicle was carrying three passengers. Njagi lost control of the vehicle when negotiating the Kanyamwe corner and hit the post, witnesses said.He fled the scene. Both his family members and the police said Njagi is yet to resurface. &ldquo;He must have been injured and is hiding somewhere as he seeks treatment. We are investigating ,&rdquo; Nyandarua Central police boss Wilson Kosgei said yesterday.